# Keep the build context small and reproducible. Crucially, never ship local
# node_modules into the image: they are platform-specific (built for the host),
# and would clobber the linux modules installed by `npm ci` inside the builder.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.git
**/.DS_Store
*.log

# Host-only artifacts not needed by the build
*.png
*.jpg
*.svg
